title: $30,000- South Ft Lauderdale Designer Waterfront Home w/ Pool and Dock
posting_body: ['A rare opportunity to rent an award-winning property that was inspired by Frank Lloyd Wright and designed by the noted architect Alberto Comas.', 'This magnificent modern custom deep-water estate home was built with the finest architectural details & materials.', "A yachtsman's dream sitting close to the SE point of the Intracoastal on a very wide canal.", 'Just a "stones throw" to the Inlet/Atlantic Ocean.', 'Amazing open water views.', 'Vacation living where you can enjoy the Gulfstream breezes from the desirable SE rear exposure with great outdoor entertaining areas.', 'The open living areas boast light filled rooms w/ high ceilings, double bedroom master suite, custom hurricane impact mahogany windows/doors, coral rock accents, stylish built-in furniture & more.', 'Available for annual ($30,000/MO) or seasonal rental (HIGHER RENT DEPENDING ON DATES).', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE PRICE.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease, background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
